\FX[FF]\AA[FFFF]\FF[1010Furea_0004]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0012]\N<Kenji>About what Guido said before... that... you confessed to
Guido...

\FX[FF]\AA[FFFF]\FF[1010Furea_0011]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0004]\N<Kenji>(...She seems to have a hard time saying it. Maybe it's
better not to press her on this...)

\FX[FF]\AA[FFFF]\FF[1010Furea_0011]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0007]\N<Kenji>Sorry, Flare. If it's hard to say, you don't have to force
yourself.

\FX[FF]\AA[FF]\FF[1010Furea_0015]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0007]\N<Flare>I apologize, Lord Kenji... it's a bit difficult to
express...

\FX[FF]\AA[FF]\FF[1010Furea_0001]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0007]\N<Flare>But, but! The one I love now is only you, my lord! Please
believe that!

\FX[FF]\AA[FFFF]\FF[1010Furea_0015]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0004]\N<Kenji>(To get her to talk, it seems I need to be trusted more by
Flare... Let's try to get closer and then ask again.)

\FX[FF]\AA[FFFF]\FF[1010Furea_0004]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0012]\N<Kenji>About what Guido said before... that... you confessed to
Guido...
\FX[FF]\AA[FF]\FF[1010Furea_0009]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0012]\N<Flare>Yes, it would be better to clarify that, wouldn't it...
\FX[FF]\AA[FF]\FF[1010Furea_0005]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0012]\N<Flare>That... previously, I was molested on the train...
\FX[FF]\AA[FFFF]\FF[1010Furea_0005]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0012]\N<Kenji>Eh...? What does that have to do with...?

\FX[FF]\AA[FF]\FF[1010Furea_0009]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0012]\N<Flare>When I was being molested and in trouble... someone helped
me. They were very kind... and that person was Guido.

\FX[FF]\AA[FFFF]\FF[1010Furea_0009]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0002]\N<Kenji>What!! So you fell for him because he saved you from the
molester...!?

\FX[FF]\AA[FF]\FF[1010Furea_0002]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0012]\N<Flare>While I was very grateful at the time, I did not fall for
him.

\FX[FF]\AA[FF]\MM[no]\FF[1010Furea_0015]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0012]\N<Flare>...because there was always a gentleman who was kind to me
nearby...
\FX[FF]\AA[FF]\FF[1010Furea_0009]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0007]\N<Flare>...In any case, Guido did save me from a molester.

\FX[FF]\AA[FF]\FF[1010Furea_0009]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0007]\N<Flare>After that, he invited me for tea several times... and then
he confessed to me.

\FX[FF]\AA[FFFF]\MMMM[jump]\FF[1010Furea_0009]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0002]\N<Kenji>...wait, what!? So it wasn't Flare who confessed, but Flare
was "confessed to"!?
\FX[FF]\AA[FF]\MM[no]\FF[1010Furea_0015]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0002]\N<Flare>Yes, that's right. It was all mixed up at that moment...
\FX[FF]\AA[FFFF]\FF[1010Furea_0015]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0002]\N<Kenji>What!? Then you should have just denied it right away?

\FX[FF]\AA[FF]\FF[1010Furea_0017]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0002]\N<Flare>Gosh!! I couldn't do that. There was the gratitude for
saving me from the molester, and the guilt of having
rejected his confession...

\FX[FF]\AA[FF]\FF[1010Furea_0015]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0002]\N<Flare>Guido has his pride too, so I couldn't just deny it on the
spot.

\FX[FF]\AA[FFFF]\FF[1010Furea_0015]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0007]\N<Kenji>So that's what it was... I thought something was off...
(Sweat)

\FX[FF]\AA[FFFF]\FF[1010Furea_0015]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0002]\N<Kenji>But, you know, right after we started dating, you said, "No
matter how many times you experience it, you never get used
to this kind of thing"...!?

\FX[FF]\AA[FF]\FF[1010Furea_0002]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0002]\N<Flare>That was because it was my first time confessing to someone,
but I have been confessed to before... That's why I said no
matter how many times you're in a situation of confession,
you never get used to it.
\FX[FF]\AA[FFFF]\FF[1010Furea_0002]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0012]\N<Kenji>So, so all my worries were just needless anxiety... (Sweat)
\FX[FF]\AA[FF]\MM[jump]\FF[1010Furea_0012]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0012]\N<Flare>Gosh!! Your trust in me is too low! Hmph!

\AA[FFFF]\FF[1010Furea_0009]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0009]\N<Kenji>I'll treat you to a Shiratama Zenzai Parfait at the station
front next time... Will you cheer up...?
\FX[FF]\AA[FF]\MM[jump]\FF[1010Furea_0014]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0009]\N<Flare>...It has to be the deluxe size.
\FX[FF]\AA[FFFF]\MMMM[no]\FF[1010Furea_0014]\FFFF[1000Kenji_0007]\N<Kenji>O-okay... If that will make you cheer up (Sweat)
